posting_body: ['The Piero is the most prestigious address, in urban-style elegance, that Los Angeles, California has to offer.', 'Experience gracious, apartment living in the heart of downtown.', 'Our superior location is moments from the financial district, fine dining, glamorous shopping, and vibrant nightlife.', 'Staples Center, Walt Disney Concert Hall, and Koreatown are just minutes from here.', 'All of the culture and arts that define Los Angeles are within reach when you live at The Piero.', 'With close proximity to the freeway, your commute in California is a breeze.', 'AMENITIES AND FEATURES', "-Separate Men's and Women's Private Dry Saunas and Steam Rooms", '-Automatic Dishwasher', '-Italian Marble Vanities', "-Four StarTrac Treadmills w/ Individual Flat-Screen TV's", '-Executive Business Center', '-Elegant Ceramic Tile Floors', "-Separate Men's and Women's Private Massage Tables", '-Two Private Computer Rooms with High Speed Internet Access', '-Easy Walk to Financial District, Fine Restaurants & Shopping', '-Designer Selected Color Schemes', '-Self-Cleaning Oven with Range', '-Crown Moldings', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'WEBSITE', '<URL>', 'ADDRESS', '616 St. Paul Ave., Los Angeles, CA 90017', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
